text: Ðis syndan þa land gemæro to cliue.
Ærost of norð tyrl on mær cumb.
Of þam cumbe on grena weg, of þam wege on cocca byrig.
Of þæra burig on hengestes heafod, of þam heafde on cippanham.
Of cippenham on tocca byrig, of þære byrce on hinde hlep.
Of hinde hlepe on myle wylla, of þære wyllan on scir wyllan.
Of þam slæde on feower wegas, of þam wegan on patacumb, þer stondað apeltreo & mapeltreo togædere gewæxen.
Of þam treowan on wulflæge, of þære læge on þa aldan dic.
Of þære dic on walhwæg, of þam wege on cælf hyl.
Of þam hylle on fina mæde, of þære mæde on hweolweg.
Of þam wege on sproges læge, of þære læge on aldan dic.
Of þære dic on alpugan þorn, of þam þorne on honta hlaw.
Of þam hlawe on swel hongre, of þone haran stan.
Of þam stane on suð tyrl, of suð tyrl to þam hors pole æt stoce.
